                  "revisionId": 2729302,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Motus Setup is additive with similar mods. For example, a Strun with a max rank Motus Setup and Shotgun Savvy and Blunderbuss will have a 5% × (1 + 100% + 90%) = 14.5% Status Chance and 7.5% × (1 + 100% + 90%) = 21.75% Critical Chance ."
                }
              },
